{"title":"Docker安装teamcity","date":"2020-05-12T19:46:21.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"May 13, 2020","L":"05/13/2020","MM-DD":"05-13"},"link":"2020/05/13/docker-install-teamcity","tags":["Docker","TeamCity"],"categories":["TeamCity"],"updated":"2020-05-17T04:21:21.510Z","content":"<h2 id=\"install-teamcity-server\">Install teamcity-server<a title=\"#install-teamcity-server\" href=\"#install-teamcity-server\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull jetbrains/teamcity-server:latest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>使用<code>docker search teamcity-server</code>命令可以搜索</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker run -itd --name teamcity -p 8111:8111 \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    -v teamcity_server:/data/teamcity_server/datadir \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    -v /opt/teamcity/logs:/opt/teamcity/logs \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    jetbrains/teamcity-server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"install-teamcity-agent\">Install teamcity-agent<a title=\"#install-teamcity-agent\" href=\"#install-teamcity-agent\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull jetbrains/teamcity-agent:latest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker run -itd --name teamcity-agent \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    -e SERVER_URL=<span class=\"string\">\"http://192.168.222.133:8111\"</span> \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    -v teamcity_agent:/data/teamcity_agent/conf \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    jetbrains/teamcity-agent</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"启动teamcity-agent\">启动teamcity-agent<a title=\"#启动teamcity-agent\" href=\"#启动teamcity-agent\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker <span class=\"built_in\">exec</span> -it teamcity-agent /bin/bash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sh run-agent.sh start</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"相关链接\">相关链接<a title=\"#相关链接\" href=\"#相关链接\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/lishan1/p/10680036.html\" title=\"TeamCity Agent安装\" target=\"_blank\">TeamCity Agent安装</a></li>\n</ul>\n","prev":{"title":"Docker常用命令","link":"2020/05/14/docker-command"},"next":{"title":"Docker安装kafka","link":"2020/05/08/docker-install-kafka"},"plink":"http://blog.arytry.com/2020/05/13/docker-install-teamcity/","toc":[{"id":"install-teamcity-server","title":"Install teamcity-server","index":"1"},{"id":"install-teamcity-agent","title":"Install teamcity-agent","index":"2","children":[{"id":"启动teamcity-agent","title":"启动teamcity-agent","index":"2.1"}]},{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","index":"3"}],"reward":true}